com.ibm.mq.explorer.ms0s.mqsceditor

Class MQSCPartitionScanner

  • java.lang.Object
    • RuleBasedPartitionScanner
      • com.ibm.mq.explorer.ms0s.mqsceditor.MQSCPartitionScanner

  • public class MQSCPartitionScanner
extends RuleBasedPartitionScanner

    This creates a RuleBasedPartitionScanner to identify the individual MQSC Commands in an MQSC document. It currently doesn't use the MQSCLanguageConfigurator to determine what the main verbs in MQSC are. This might be complicated to implement, given that we also need to build constants for each partition type. It could be looked into.
